</div>
<div class="jumbotron background-image-1">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 white">
                <h1>Purchase Consulting</h1>
                <p class="lead" >Be connected with an expert, intelligent, helpful and friendly consultant who cares about your achievement.</p>
                <h3>Our Guarantee</h3>
                <p class="lead" >If you aren't satisfied with our service for any reason, <span style="color:#52A552">we will refund your money, no questions asked.</span></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset-2 white">
                <p>Be more productive</p>
                <p>Balance your time</p>
                <p>Secure your finances</p>
                <p>Lose weight</p>
            </div>
